  "faqs": [
    {
      "question": "What is the NTPC Green Energy IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>NTPC Green Energy IPO<!-- --> is a <b>main-board<!-- --> <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> of <!-- -->925925926<!-- --> equity shares</b> of the face value of ₹<!-- -->10<!-- --> aggregating up to ₹<!-- -->10,000.00<!-- --> Crores. The issue is priced at <span>₹108 per share</span>. The minimum order quantity is <!-- -->138<!-- -->.</p><p>The <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> <b>opens on <!-- -->November 19, 2024</b>, and <b>closes on <!-- -->November 22, 2024</b>.</p><p>Kfin Technologies Limited<!-- --> is the registrar for the <!-- -->IPO<!-- -->. The shares are proposed to be listed on <!-- -->BSE, NSE<!-- -->.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply in NTPC Green Energy IPO through Zerodha?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Zerodha customers can apply online in <!-- -->NTPC Green Energy IPO<!-- --> using UPI as a payment gateway. Zerodha customers can apply in <!-- -->NTPC Green Energy IPO<!-- --> by login into Zerodha Console (back office) and submitting an IPO application form.</p><p><strong>Steps to apply in <!-- -->NTPC Green Energy IPO<!-- --> through Zerodha</strong></p><ol><li>Visit the Zerodha website and login to Console.</li><li>Go to Portfolio and click the IPOs link.</li><li>Go to the '<!-- -->NTPC Green Energy IPO<!-- -->' row and click the 'Bid' button.</li><li>Enter your UPI ID, Quantity, and Price.</li><li>Submit IPO application form.</li><li>Visit the UPI App (net banking or BHIM) to approve the mandate.</li></ol><p>Visit <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Application Process Review\">Zerodha IPO Application Process Review</a> for more detail.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When NTPC Green Energy IPO will open?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The NTPC Green Energy IPO opens on November 19, 2024 and closes on November 22, 2024.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "What is the lot size of NTPC Green Energy IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>NTPC Green Energy IPO<!-- --> <b>lot size is <!-- -->138</b>, and the <b>minimum amount required is <span>₹14,904</span></b>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply for NTPC Green Energy IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>You can apply in <!-- -->NTPC Green Energy IPO<!-- --> online using either <a href=\"/article/upi-payment-option-ipo-application-explained/382/\">UPI</a> or ASBA as a payment method. ASBA IPO application is available in the net banking of your bank account. UPI IPO application is offered by brokers who don't offer banking services. Read more detail about applying IPO online through <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Review\"><b>Zerodha</b></a>, <a href=\"/broker/upstox/ipo/33/\" title=\"Upstox IPO Review\">Upstox</a>, <a href=\"/broker/5paisa/ipo/4/\" title=\"5Paisa IPO Review\">5Paisa</a>, <a href=\"/broker/edelweiss_broking/ipo/34/\" title=\"Nuvama IPO Review\">Nuvama</a>, <a href=\"/broker/hdfc-securities/ipo/6/\" title=\"HDFC Bank IPO Review\">HDFC Bank</a>, and <a href=\"/broker/sbi-capital/ipo/19/\" title=\"SBI Capital IPO Review\">SBI Bank</a>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When is NTPC Green Energy IPO allotment?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The finalization of Basis of Allotment for <!-- -->NTPC Green Energy IPO<!-- --> will be done on <!-- -->Monday, November 25, 2024<!-- -->, and the allotted shares will be credited to your demat account by <!-- -->Tuesday, November 26, 2024<!-- -->. Check the <a href=\"/ipo_allotment_status/ntpc-green-energy-ipo/1902/\" title=\"NTPC Green Energy IPO Allotment Status\">NTPC Green Energy IPO<!-- --> allotment status</a>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
